WEBVTT

00:23.050 --> 00:25.140
-你找到我的书了吗? -找到了
-Were you able to find my book? -Yeah.

00:25.150 --> 00:26.840
但有个家伙出现
But there was this guy.

00:26.850 --> 00:28.150
把书抢走了
He took it.

00:28.150 --> 00:28.840
他让我告诉你
He said to tell you

00:28.850 --> 00:30.840
斯科菲尔德的哥哥拿了那本书
that Scofield's brother has it now.

00:30.850 --> 00:32.140
你得把他们救出来
You have to break them out of there.

00:32.150 --> 00:33.450
LJ
LJ

00:33.650 --> 00:34.750
莎拉
Sara

00:37.250 --> 00:39.140
别再尝试这么做
You're never going to try anything like that again.

00:39.150 --> 00:40.040
只是为了确认
But just to make sure,

00:40.050 --> 00:42.250
我在车库里给你留了点东西
I left you a little something in the garage.

01:37.950 --> 01:40.650
窗外有什么比自由更吸引人的东西么?
What's so interesting out there, other than our freedom?

01:40.650 --> 01:43.950
出逃者还活着 证明围墙上没电
Finds are alive, so the fence is dead

01:43.950 --> 01:46.140
是么?这里每个人都知道那围墙没用
Yeah? Everyone in here knows is that fence doesn't work,

01:46.150 --> 01:47.140
但这也改变不了什么
and it doesn't mean a bloody thing,

01:47.150 --> 01:48.340
因为外面有士兵把守
because there are soldiers out there

01:48.350 --> 01:50.240
只要你在30码内他们就会把你射死
that'll shoot you dead before you get within 30 yards of it.

01:50.250 --> 01:52.750
我得好好计划一下了 不是么?
Well, I guess I got a lot of work to do, don't I?

01:53.650 --> 01:54.940
听着 老兄 我知道你抢了我的书
Listen, mate, I get what you're doing with my book.

01:54.950 --> 01:57.340
他们抓走了你的女友 而你抢走了他们要的东西
They hold your girlfriend, you hold what they want.

01:57.350 --> 01:59.340
互惠互利 Churchill 101法案
Countering needs. Churchill 101.

01:59.350 --> 02:00.540
马上那些杂种就要来问我
Soon those bastards are going to ask me

02:00.550 --> 02:02.240
他们所要的 我了解了多少
what progress I've made in figuring out what they want,

02:02.250 --> 02:05.550
我就要说完全不了解 因为林肯·布鲁斯把书抢走了
and I'm going to say nil, 'cause Lincoln Burrows has the book.

02:05.650 --> 02:06.750
知道么?
You know what?

02:08.150 --> 02:08.740
威胁
Threatening the brother

02:08.750 --> 02:10.040
要帮你越狱的人的哥哥
of the guy who's supposed to get you out of here

02:10.050 --> 02:11.240
并不是个好主意
might not be the smartest move.

02:11.250 --> 02:13.350
我没有威胁你 我们在同一条船上
I'm not threatening we're on the same team.

02:13.450 --> 02:14.640
但如果我们因为那本书纠缠不清
But if we play games with that book,

02:14.650 --> 02:17.950
那些想让我出去的人会采取行动的
people who want me out of here will take action

02:18.250 --> 02:20.950
"我不在乎你们做什么 就怕你们什么也不做"
"I never worry about action, only inaction."

02:21.350 --> 02:22.840
根据Churchill 101法案
Churchill 101.

02:22.850 --> 02:25.650
如我所说 现在我有很多事要做
Now, like I said, I got a lot of work to do.

02:56.150 --> 02:57.650
林肯 你还好吧?
Linc, you all right?

02:58.750 --> 02:59.540
对不起 老弟
I'm sorry, man.

02:59.550 --> 03:02.340
都是那东西 它快找到我了
Just all this stuff it's starting to get to me.

03:02.350 --> 03:03.350
知道么?
You know?

03:06.750 --> 03:09.640
听着 我们的境遇很快会改变
Listen, our situation could change very, very soon.

03:09.650 --> 03:11.450
那个监狱掘墓人
The grave digger for the prison.

03:11.650 --> 03:13.440
你得和他联系上
I need you to reach out to him.

03:13.450 --> 03:14.640
告诉他什么?
And tell him what?

03:14.650 --> 03:15.840
都写在上面了
It's all written down.

03:15.850 --> 03:17.450
我们现在就得采取行动
But we got to get started now.

03:21.150 --> 03:22.950
你有什么没告诉我的?
What are you not telling me?

03:23.750 --> 03:24.240
所有人
All these people

03:24.250 --> 03:25.850
都因为我而受伤害
that have been hurt because of me.

03:26.650 --> 03:30.940
我很抱歉 迈克
I'm so sorry, Michael.

03:30.950 --> 03:33.050
这是他们造成的 不是你
They did this, not you.

03:33.250 --> 03:34.150
好吗?
Okay?

03:34.650 --> 03:35.950
这不是你的错
It's not your fault.

03:36.650 --> 03:38.250
找到那个掘墓人
Just get to the grave digger.

03:39.450 --> 03:41.250
我感觉我们没多少时间了
I feel like we're running out of time.

04:21.950 --> 04:23.050
莎拉
Sara.

