这场较量中我只是一个棋子 林肯
I am just a soldier in this war, Lincoln,

05:28.000 --> 05:29.200
和你一样
just like you.

05:30.600 --> 05:33.500
我并不想那么做的
I did not want to do that.

05:34.100 --> 05:36.190
你能理解
Can you even comprehend the intimacy

05:36.200 --> 05:38.900
我对那个女人下手时的感受吗?
of the mechanics of what I had to do to that woman?

05:39.600 --> 05:41.100
那太恐怖了
It's horrible

05:42.500 --> 05:44.700
现在 如果你和你弟弟停止耍花招
Now, if you and your brother are done playing games,

05:44.800 --> 05:46.300
LJ会没事的
LJ will be fine.

05:46.400 --> 05:50.390
我最不想做的事是把他一块块寄给你
If not, the last thing I want to do send millions pieces of him to you

05:50.400 --> 05:52.290
但如果你逼我
But if you push me

05:52.300 --> 05:55.900
即使没逼那么狠 我会这么做的
and not even that far, I will.

05:57.700 --> 05:59.200
你叫我干什么我就干什么
I'll do anything you want.

05:59.200 --> 06:00.700
别伤害我的儿子就好
Just don't hurt my son.

06:01.300 --> 06:02.600
这些都取决于你
That's really up to you.

06:05.300 --> 06:07.290
我知道这几天很难熬
I know the past few days have been hard,

06:07.300 --> 06:08.600
我也一样
for me, as well.

06:09.300 --> 06:10.900
如果你想聊聊
If you want to talk about it,

06:11.200 --> 06:13.100
我理解这痛苦的感觉
I know what this pain feels like.

06:13.400 --> 06:14.790
我只想把那个人搞出Sona
I just want to get your boy out of Sona

06:14.800 --> 06:16.400
然后接回我儿子
and get my son back.

06:17.700 --> 06:18.900
迈克有计划了
Michael's got a plan.

06:18.900 --> 06:20.100
我需要细节
I need details.

06:20.300 --> 06:20.990
我们得把某个
We need to bring someone

06:21.000 --> 06:23.100
在监狱工作的人拉拢过来
who works at the prison onto the team.

06:23.100 --> 06:23.900
谁?
Who?

06:24.300 --> 06:25.600
掘墓人
The grave digger.

06:26.100 --> 06:27.300
去做吧
Get it done.

06:29.700 --> 06:31.800
林肯 我需要那本书
Lincoln, I'm going to need that book.

06:32.700 --> 06:35.600
中情局把你给我的那本做了笔迹鉴定
The Company did handwriting analysis on the one you gave me,

06:36.200 --> 06:38.300
你的字迹从高中以来就没变过
and yours hasn't changed since high school.

06:48.500 --> 06:50.000
我们只是棋子 林肯
Just soldiers, Linc.

06:50.400 --> 06:52.800
代表不同方 但本质是一样的
Different armies, but soldiers just the same.

07:11.000 --> 07:12.200
打得好
Nice.

07:13.000 --> 07:14.500
我在学校里是最棒的
I was the best in my school.

07:14.500 --> 07:15.500
女校?
All girls?

07:16.400 --> 07:16.890
去你的
Kiss my ass,

07:16.900 --> 07:17.900
老兄
bro.

07:19.400 --> 07:21.500
20美元赌你没法再投进
20 bucks says you can't do that again.

07:21.700 --> 07:23.000
-好的 -等一下
-Bet. -Wait.

07:24.600 --> 07:25.800
根据风向调整
Adjust for wind.

07:26.200 --> 07:27.000
闭嘴
Shut up.

07:30.200 --> 07:32.200
向外偏一点就好了
Just a bit outside.

07:33.300 --> 07:35.900
老兄 你知道我现在没有钱
Hey, bro, you know I don't have that kind of verde lying around.

07:36.500 --> 07:37.900
需要点时间
It's going to take a while.

07:38.000 --> 07:40.000
问题在于 我没有时间了
Well, the thing is, I don't have a while.

07:40.000 --> 07:42.400
-所以 除非 -别 别再拉拢我了
-So, unless -No, no more favors.

07:43.300 --> 07:44.290
好吧
All right.

07:44.300 --> 07:45.890
我能借你的十字架一用么?
Can I borrow that cross of yours?

07:45.900 --> 07:49.500
-就拿那个做交换吧 -这是我爸给我的
-I'll take it in trade. -My dad gave me this.

07:50.000 --> 07:51.490
还有 那甚至不是金的
Besides, it's not even real gold.

07:51.500 --> 07:52.600
这正是我需要它的原因
That's why I need it.

07:53.900 --> 07:54.690
听着 我会还给你的 好吗?
Look, I'll give it back, okay?

07:54.700 --> 07:56.000
只是借
It's just a loan.

07:58.400 --> 07:59.900
给我吧
Come on.

08:08.200 --> 08:10.000
这次 我想知道原因
This time, I want to know why.

08:21.300 --> 08:22.700
又是灯
It's light again.

08:23.600 --> 08:25.390
有人正在破坏暴动后
Someone's getting fat off of everythg I built

08:25.400 --> 08:26.800
我所建立的一切
while I rot in here.

08:26.800 --> 08:27.490
别郁闷了
Don't get upset,

08:27.500 --> 08:28.700
拜托
patron

08:30.400 --> 08:32.300
我只有几个小时
I only have a few more hours.

08:32.300 --> 08:33.600
让我们好好享受下
Let's be nice.

08:52.000 --> 08:54.100
该死的
This motherless bitch.

09:24.700 --> 09:26.400
阿历克斯?
Alex?

09:30.500 --> 09:31.490
你刚到这?
You just get here?

09:31.500 --> 09:32.400
是的
Yes.

09:35.500 --> 09:35.890
听好了
Listen,

09:35.900 --> 09:40.500
我一直在权衡 决定让你入伙
I've been thinking about and, uh, you're in.

09:41.800 --> 09:42.490
我算入伙了
I'm in.

09:42.500 --> 09:43.790
好吧
Okay.

09:43.800 --> 09:45.800
-就这么简单? -是的
-Just like that? -Right.

09:45.800 --> 09:47.600
我别无选择 不是吗?
I really don't have a choice, do I?

09:48.800 --> 09:49.590
你怎么计划的?
What's the plan?

09:49.600 --> 09:50.700
我正在想办法
I'm working on it.

09:51.400 --> 09:53.390
与此同时 你也可以帮上我的忙
Meanwhile, I could use your help.

09:53.400 --> 09:54.200
你需要什么?
What do you need?

09:54.300 --> 09:55.800
黑色毡尖笔
A black felt-tipped pen.

09:55.900 --> 09:57.490
-一支钢笔? -没错
-A pen? -Yeah.

09:57.500 --> 09:58.590
-为什么? -有些文件
-Why? -Some documents

09:58.600 --> 10:00.300
需要做些改动
that need altering.

10:00.500 --> 10:02.990
稍后再给你解释 我现在就要那支笔
I'll explain it to you later, but right now, I need that pen.

10:03.000 --> 10:05.890
-行吗? -好的
-Okay? -Yeah.

10:05.900 --> 10:07.090
我还要对你说的是
And I'll tell you what else I need.

10:07.100 --> 10:08.890
我要你跟我们步调一致
I need you to get your act together.

10:08.900 --> 10:10.190
我需要你控制好自己
I need you to bring yourself

10:10.200 --> 10:12.590
因为你那样很夺人眼球
under control, because you're attracting attention,

10:12.600 --> 10:14.700
而那是我们不想看到的
and that we don't need.

10:14.700 --> 10:16.200
我能控制好自己
I'm under control.

10:16.700 --> 10:17.800
你当然可以
Of course you are.

10:27.400 --> 10:29.700
这就是用电负荷过大的下场
This is what happens when a system is overloaded.

10:30.800 --> 10:32.400
看到吗?
See? Look.

10:33.900 --> 10:35.600
-该死 -断电了
-Son of a -Power is out.

10:36.800 --> 10:37.790
搞定它
Fix it.

10:37.800 --> 10:39.200
我只是个卡车司机
I'm a truck driver.

10:46.900 --> 10:47.900
嘿 阿历克斯
Hey, Alex.

10:50.100 --> 10:51.990
很高兴找到你 就是来看看
Hey, glad I found ya. Just wanted to see how

10:52.000 --> 10:54.200
-你在这过得怎样 -非常好
-you're holding up in here. -Just dandy.

10:54.400 --> 10:56.690
我也经历过段受煎熬的日子
Yeah, well, I've been having a tough time of it myself.

10:56.700 --> 10:57.790
但我想我们的命不该这样
And I was figuring shouldn't be that way

10:57.800 --> 10:59.690
我们可是唯一的正直人士
for us, seeing as how we're the only lawmen here

10:59.700 --> 11:00.800
在这个阴曹地府里
in Taco Hell.

11:01.000 --> 11:02.990
嘿 等会儿 阿历克斯
Hey, whoa, hang on a second there, Alex.

11:03.000 --> 11:04.290
你和我 我们可是一队的
You and me we were a team

11:04.300 --> 11:05.190
还记得我们在外面的时候吗?
on the outside, remember?

11:05.200 --> 11:07.890
我是你的部下 现在依然对你忠心不二
I was your dog, and I still got a lot of bark left in me.

11:07.900 --> 11:10.090
布拉德 我很忙 你到底想怎样?
I'm busy, Brad. What do you want?

11:10.100 --> 11:12.490
你和斯科菲尔德在计划逃跑是吧?
You and Scofield you're up to something, right?

11:12.500 --> 11:14.500
你可以告诉我 兄弟之间没有隔阂
You can tell me, one badge to another.

11:14.500 --> 11:15.500
我能帮上忙
I can help.

11:16.000 --> 11:17.800
你有黑色毡尖笔吗?
Do you have a black felt-tipped pen?

11:18.800 --> 11:19.990
我没有
Not on me.

11:20.000 --> 11:21.500
那你帮不了我
Then you can't help me.

11:39.900 --> 11:40.900
我都知道了
I know.

11:42.100 --> 11:42.590
你知道什么了?
You know what?

11:42.600 --> 11:44.390
我知道你在计划越狱
I know you're trying to escape from here

11:44.400 --> 11:46.200
和那个叫斯科菲尔德的家伙
with that man, Scofield.

11:46.400 --> 11:48.600
-宝贝 -求你不要欺瞒我
Sweetheart Please, don't lie to me.

11:48.700 --> 11:50.800
林肯·布鲁斯把一切都告诉了我
Lincoln Burrows, he told me everything.

11:54.100 --> 11:57.390
有些非常有权势的人希望我出来
There are some very powerful people that want me out of here.

11:57.400 --> 11:59.990
-他们让那哥俩救我出去 -为何?
And they want those brothers to get me out. Why?

12:00.000 --> 12:01.300
我也不确定
I'm not sure.

12:01.500 --> 12:04.100
应该和我在西雅图看到的场景有关系
Has something to do with a charter I did in Seattle.

12:04.100 --> 12:05.190
我只知道他们的最终目的
What I do know is their end game

12:05.200 --> 12:08.000
和我们的一样 就是让我逃出这鬼地方
is exa the same as ours, and that's me out of this hellhole.

12:08.400 --> 12:09.490
一旦成功了
And once that happens,

12:09.500 --> 12:12.200
你和我就会消失 永远销声匿迹
you and I will disappear forever.

12:12.300 --> 12:14.290
但是我不想让你趟这趟浑水
But I don't want to involve you in this mess.

12:14.300 --> 12:15.090
我想帮你啊
I want to help.

12:15.100 --> 12:15.990
那太危险了
That's way too dangerous.

12:16.000 --> 12:17.390
詹姆斯我不是在请求你的批准
I'm not asking your permission, James.

12:17.400 --> 12:18.700
我是在告诉你
I'm telling you.

12:18.700 --> 12:20.490
我自己一人也能搞定
I can do this on my own,

12:20.500 --> 12:21.890
或者你可以把你知道的告诉我
or you can tell me what you know

12:21.900 --> 12:23.600
然后我们共同解决
and we can work it through together.

12:25.900 --> 12:28.200
我对发生的事情也不明白
I don't understand everything that's going on,

12:28.300 --> 12:29.390
但是那对兄弟 他们显然试图
but these brothers, they're obviously trying

12:29.400 --> 12:30.990
从我身上打探出信息来
to find out what they can about me.

12:31.000 --> 12:32.890
我们看看能从他们身上了解多少
Let's see what we can discover about them.

12:32.900 --> 12:34.790
弄清楚他们的计划 了解真实目的
Find out what their plan is, see what they're all about.

12:34.800 --> 12:37.090
他们帮你越狱 你却不信他们?
They're trying to get you out, and you don't trust them?

12:37.100 --> 12:39.000
我谁都不信任
I don't trust any of these guys.

12:39.100 --> 12:40.500
你也不该相信
And yoshouldn't, either.

12:41.100 --> 12:42.690
如果你坚持要跟此事
If you insist on getting into this,

12:42.700 --> 12:44.700
向我保证你会加倍小心
promise me you'll be careful.

12:44.900 --> 12:45.990
因为如果你出什么三长两短
Because God knows I will die

12:46.000 --> 12:47.700
我也不会苟活的
if anything happens to you.

12:51.000 --> 12:51.800
嘿
Hey.

13:11.100 --> 13:12.100
迈克
Michael.

13:15.200 --> 13:16.100
拿着
Here.

13:17.200 --> 13:20.500
我说过我要的是黑色毡尖笔
I said I need a black felt-tipped pen.

13:24.500 --> 13:25.700
那是黑色的
That's black.

13:25.700 --> 13:27.000
这不是我需要的
It's not what I need.

13:28.400 --> 13:29.500
继续去找
Keep looking.

13:33.800 --> 13:35.400
他在耍你
He's playing you.

13:36.500 --> 13:38.000
他在耍你
He's playing you.

13:38.200 --> 13:41.100
不要相信他
Do not trust him.

13:53.000 --> 13:54.900
你那美国佬兄弟
Your amigo, the American.

13:56.600 --> 13:59.100
他是建筑工程师 是吗?
He's a builder, an engineer, no?

13:59.100 --> 14:01.000
老大 他可不是我的朋友
He's no amigo of mine, boss.

14:01.400 --> 14:02.790
相信我 你绝不希望
And trust me, you do not want

14:02.800 --> 14:03.690
和他扯上关系
to get under the covers with that

14:03.700 --> 14:05.500
回答我 是或不是工程师?
Is he or is he not an engineer?

14:05.600 --> 14:07.000
好吧 是的 但是
Well, yeah, but

14:10.800 --> 14:11.900
斯科菲尔德
Scofield.

14:12.900 --> 14:14.000
什么事?
Yeah?

14:14.400 --> 14:15.890
你懂电路吗?
What do you know about the electricity?

14:15.900 --> 14:17.800
停电时候就会懂吧
Only that we don't have any right now.

14:18.500 --> 14:19.700
和你说件事情
Let me tell you something.

14:19.900 --> 14:23.090
这部手机能让食物运进来
This phone keeps all the food coming to the gate.

14:23.100 --> 14:25.190
这样才能保障Sona监狱的正常运转
It keeps my business running, it keeps Sona running.

14:25.200 --> 14:26.290
断电了 电话也就不能用了
Electricity die, phone die.

14:26.300 --> 14:29.300
-电话没了我们也完蛋 -我们完蛋 你也完蛋
Phone die, we die. We die or youdie?

14:30.100 --> 14:31.090
小子 你知识够丰富
Boy, you have enough

14:31.100 --> 14:32.890
但是人不够聪明
education, but you're not being smart.

14:32.900 --> 14:35.790
我来找你 是给你机会
Now, I come to you, that is an opportunity.

14:35.800 --> 14:37.590
放聪明些 好好把握机会
Be wise and take advantage.

14:37.600 --> 14:40.200
现在回答我 能修复电路吗
Now, can you fix the electricity

14:40.200 --> 14:41.690
就像你搞定水源那样
just like you fixed the water?

14:41.700 --> 14:42.990
这可没有那么简单
It's not that simple.

14:43.000 --> 14:44.990
水管是在监狱里的
The water pipes are inside the prison.

14:45.000 --> 14:47.590
电线却可能是在地底
The electrical lines are probably running underground

14:47.600 --> 14:49.490
沿着墙外排布的
along an exterior wall,

14:49.500 --> 14:51.100
意味着电线在外面的
which means they're out there somewhere

14:51.900 --> 14:53.200
某个禁入区
in no-man's-land.

14:53.900 --> 14:56.290
那你能恢复电力吗?
So, you can fix the power?

14:56.300 --> 14:58.190
上次我看到他们射杀了出去的人
Last I checked, they shoot prisoners who go out there.

14:58.200 --> 14:59.900
所以我觉得答案是"不行"
So I'm thinking the answer is"no."

15:02.300 --> 15:03.800
听我说
You listen to me,

15:04.100 --> 15:06.200
听清楚了 小子
and you listen closely, water boy.

15:06.200 --> 15:08.400
不管情况是否相似 不管有没有士兵
Like it or not, soldiers or not,

15:08.900 --> 15:11.700
你要去禁入区
you're going out into no-man's-land.

15:19.000 --> 15:20.500
这是自杀式任务
It's a suicide mission.

15:20.500 --> 15:21.590
我要打几个电话
I'll make some calls.

15:21.600 --> 15:24.000
-你要确保我安全 -尽我所能吧
And you're going to keep meafe? As best I can.

15:24.000 --> 15:25.190
我觉得我做不到
I don't think I can do this.

15:25.200 --> 15:28.400
不 不 不 你会帮我的
No, no, no, no, no. You will help me with this.

15:28.400 --> 15:29.790
我也会为你做点事情的
Look, I will do something for you.

15:29.800 --> 15:31.290
我会给你一个新枕头
I'll get you a new pillow,

15:31.300 --> 15:33.500
鹅毛的 像我的那样 或者一台小电视
goose-feather like mine, or a small TV.

15:35.000 --> 15:36.000
好吧
All right.

15:36.700 --> 15:37.800
给我那间房间
Get me that.

15:39.800 --> 15:42.890
-为什么? -这里可以享受早上第一缕阳光
Why? It's the first one to get sunlight in the morning.

15:42.900 --> 15:45.900
你给我那间囚室 我给你电力
You get me that cell, I'll get you electricity.

15:59.500 --> 16:00.600
好啊林肯
Hey, Linc.

16:11.400 --> 16:14.300
兄弟 我很快就要离开你了
Look, bro, um, I'm going to be out of your way real soon.

16:14.400 --> 16:17.390
我看到哥伦比亚招移民工人的小广告
I saw these flyers for migrant workers in Colombia.

16:17.400 --> 16:18.290
现在是咖啡豆的收获季节
It's coffee bean season,

16:18.300 --> 16:19.890
他们让巴拿马人去干活
and they're letting Panamanians in,

16:19.900 --> 16:23.000
所以我想 换张身份证我就可以过关了
so I figure, with a good ID, I can pass.

16:23.800 --> 16:25.300
大巴今天发车 好吗?
Bus leaves today, okay?

16:25.400 --> 16:28.790
好吧 在你离开这儿之前 伙计 我
All right, well, before you get out of here, man, I

16:28.800 --> 16:31.300
我要见个人 我需要一个翻译
I'm meeting someone, and I need a translator.

16:32.000 --> 16:34.090
林肯我很欣赏你做的每件事
Linc, uh I appreciate everything you've done

16:34.100 --> 16:34.990
只需要几个小时
It'll just be a couple hours.

16:35.000 --> 16:36.400
几个小时就够了
Just a couple hours, that's it.

16:37.300 --> 16:40.090
我15岁时 我堂兄给了我一份工作
When I was 15, my cousin told me about a job that only lasts

16:40.100 --> 16:43.090
只消几小时 我却在少教所待了三个月
a few hours and, uh, I got three months in juvie.

16:43.100 --> 16:44.190
没有你我做不到
I can't do this without you.

16:44.200 --> 16:45.790
我在巴拿马 我不会说西班牙语
I'm in Panama, I don't speak the language

16:45.800 --> 16:47.590
可是我也不能错过大巴
And I can't miss that bus.

16:47.600 --> 16:49.390
我要挣钱 寄回家
I'm going ake money and send it home.

16:49.400 --> 16:50.990
偷偷摸摸也好 我要做爸爸了 林肯
Underground or not, I'm going to be a dad, Linc,

16:51.000 --> 16:53.400
你和其他人不一样 应该理解
and you out of all people should understand that.

17:08.700 --> 17:10.500
我和詹姆斯聊过
I spoke to James.

17:11.800 --> 17:13.290
他确认了你和我说的
He confirmed what you told me

17:13.300 --> 17:14.500
越狱的事情
about the escape.

17:16.000 --> 17:18.590
你和我 都有关心的人
You and I, we both have people in there

17:18.600 --> 17:19.800
在那里
we care about.

17:22.100 --> 17:25.000
求求你 让我帮你吧
Please let me help you.

17:26.500 --> 17:28.300
你的西班牙语和英语一样好吗?
Your Spanish as good as your English?

17:31.100 --> 17:31.790
是的 长官
Yes, Colonel.

17:31.800 --> 17:33.900
我要你帮个忙
I just have one favor to ask.

17:34.200 --> 17:35.700
只是要在门外
It's just outside of the gate.

17:36.000 --> 17:38.000
你可以带你的人来
You, you can bring your men.

17:39.600 --> 17:41.000
电话没电了
The phone dying.

17:45.000 --> 17:46.300
给他一个
Make him one.

17:57.800 --> 17:58.900
就那么点?
This is it?

17:59.700 --> 18:01.200
不是每个人都有
Not everyone has it yet.

18:01.400 --> 18:03.800
我们延迟了一星期 所以还有些时间
We let credit go a week, and there is still time.

18:04.500 --> 18:06.190
钱在你那里
The money's in your veins, addicto.

18:06.200 --> 18:10.600
没有 老大 我没用过 我发誓
No, patron. I don't use anymore. I swear to you.

18:11.500 --> 18:12.690
我发誓 没有
I swear to you. No.

18:12.700 --> 18:13.700
我发誓 我发誓
I swear to you. I swear to you.

18:22.100 --> 18:23.700
振作 伙计 振作
Chin up, pal o' mine, Chin up.

18:31.200 --> 18:32.300
知道了 长官
Si Colonel.

18:32.800 --> 18:34.190
好的 谢谢长官
Yes, thank you, Colonel.

18:34.200 --> 18:35.200
我们马上就到
We'll be right there.

18:36.100 --> 18:37.000
跟我来
Come with me.

18:41.900 --> 18:43.300
对不起 你有
Excuse me. Do you, um

18:44.000 --> 18:46.500
你有钢笔吗?
Do you have a-a, a pen?

18:47.200 --> 18:48.800
钢笔 不是
n. Pen. Not, um

18:48.900 --> 18:50.090
不是那刷子
Not not the brush

18:50.100 --> 18:51.490
是钢笔 写字的钢笔
but the pen. Pen. Pen.

18:51.500 --> 18:52.590
没有 只有绘画笔
No, pintura.

18:52.600 --> 18:54.100
是的 绘画笔
Yeah, yeah, pintura. Yeah.

19:11.100 --> 19:12.300
他要离开你
He's leaving you.

19:12.500 --> 19:14.190
他要离开你 他走了
He's leaving you, he'll be gone,

19:14.200 --> 19:17.200
你要困在这个迷宫里了
and you'll be stuck in this maze forever.

19:23.700 --> 19:25.590
谢谢你帮我们安排这些 长官
Thank you for arranging this for us, Colonel.

19:25.600 --> 19:27.390
我也要拿走一些东西
I'm getting something out of this as well,

19:27.400 --> 19:28.500
我保证
I assure you.

19:28.600 --> 19:30.900
你确定你可以解决电力问题?
You know you can fix this electric problem?

19:31.800 --> 19:33.790
在开始挖之前我不能确定
I won't know for sure until we can start digging,

19:33.800 --> 19:36.500
但是 我想可以的
but yes, I think so.

19:37.400 --> 19:39.490
我的人会打爆你的头
My men will shoot you in t back of the head

19:39.500 --> 19:41.400
如果你老看着围墙的话 明白?
if you so much as look at the fence, eh?

19:42.000 --> 19:45.390
还有你 老大 如果有事情发生
And you, patron, if anything goes wrong.

19:45.400 --> 19:47.590
不仅仅是他小命不保
it will not only be his life that is lost.

19:47.600 --> 19:49.200
你也得承担责任
You have my word on that.

19:49.200 --> 19:50.700
长官 不用担心
No worries, Colonel.

19:51.900 --> 19:53.500
我会让这小子规规矩矩的
I'll keep this boy in line.

19:57.600 --> 19:58.690
我也来挖
I'll dig.

19:58.700 --> 19:59.990
我不要你帮忙
I don't need your help.

20:00.000 --> 20:01.590
来吧 不要骄傲
Hey, come on, now, don't be proud.

20:01.600 --> 20:03.500
我昨天恰好听到了你的谈话
I heard you talking just yesterday.

20:03.600 --> 20:04.990
和马宏的谈话
Talking to Mahone.

20:05.000 --> 20:07.800
你知道 关于美国人如何联合起来
You know, about how us Americans should stick together.

20:07.800 --> 20:12.100
也会帮我离开这里的 对吧 迈克?
help me down the road, right, Mikey?

20:18.300 --> 20:21.100
这是什么 66年还是67年的?
What is it, a '66 or a '67?

20:21.200 --> 20:22.790
-什么? -你的车
erdon? Your car.

20:22.800 --> 20:24.800
他在问你的气缸的年代
El quiere saber el ano.

20:24.800 --> 20:26.200
看这里
ste aqui?

20:26.600 --> 20:28.800
对 是66年的
Pues, es un '66.

20:29.100 --> 20:30.390
还是我做的贡献
Y es mi preciosa.

20:30.400 --> 20:31.490
66年的
66.

20:31.500 --> 20:34.200
恩 这是什么 325马力?
Uh-huh. What is it, 325 horses?

20:34.300 --> 20:35.490
多少马力的
aballos de fuerza?

20:35.500 --> 20:38.000
375马力
375.

20:38.200 --> 20:40.200
375马力
375.

20:41.200 --> 20:43.000
抱歉
Perdon a me, srita. Mm-hmm.

20:46.400 --> 20:46.990
-他在说什么? -他认出我了 但是
What's he saying? recognizes me, but

20:47.000 --> 20:49.790
他没意识到那是在监狱
he doesn't realize it was at the prison.

20:49.800 --> 20:51.390
问问他 是否想赚点钱
Ask him does he want to make enough cash

20:51.400 --> 20:53.500
在下周把车子重新上个漆
to get this car cherry by next week?

21:01.900 --> 21:04.200
他知道我们不是在讨论车子
He knows we're not talking about cars.

21:04.700 --> 21:06.100
没错
That's right.

21:08.800 --> 21:10.290
斯科菲尔德 我知道你要离开这里
Come on, Scofield, I know you're getting out of here.

21:10.300 --> 21:11.690
我听到了关于你和英国佬的事情
I heard it all about you and the limey.

21:11.700 --> 21:13.490
老兄 我只是在修复电力
I'm just fixing the electricity, Boss.

21:13.500 --> 21:15.890
是的 我没有伙伴 因为我很挑剔
Yeah, right, and I'm just single 'cause I'm choosy.

21:15.900 --> 21:17.790
别逼我到处说我知道的
Don't make me tell anyone what I know.

21:17.800 --> 21:19.090
你知道了什么?
What is it you think you know?

21:19.100 --> 21:20.890
所谓"公司"的人想让你进来这儿
Somebody called"the Company"wanted you in here

21:20.900 --> 21:22.390
和那个叫惠斯勒的家伙合作
to work with that Whistler guy.

21:22.400 --> 21:24.390
-没错吧? -什么"公司"?
Am I warm? What's the Company?

21:24.400 --> 21:25.490
他们要惠斯勒干吗?
What do they want with Whistler?

21:25.500 --> 21:27.500
我不知道 但是你知道
I don't know, but you do.

21:28.200 --> 21:30.090
看来你知道的并不多
Doesn't sound like you know much after all.

21:30.100 --> 21:30.790
我不需要知道
I don't need to know

21:30.800 --> 21:31.890
臭气熏天的时候
how to change a diaper

21:31.900 --> 21:34.200
要怎么换尿布
to know when it stinks to high hell.

21:34.400 --> 21:35.990
你是有目的的 斯科菲尔德
You're doing something here, Scofield.

21:36.000 --> 21:38.000
没错 是的
You're right. I am.

21:38.300 --> 21:40.400
我在恢复供电
I'm fixing the electricity.

21:40.600 --> 21:41.990
你要来帮忙挖吗?
Now, you wanted to help dig?

21:42.000 --> 21:43.200
那就挖吧
Dig.

22:06.700 --> 22:09.300
就是这儿了
Hey, this is it.

22:24.200 --> 22:26.190
我想我们不只是在做电工活吧
I assume we're doing more than just than playing electrician.

22:26.200 --> 22:27.500
别担心
Don't worry.

22:28.100 --> 22:30.100
我知道我在干什么
We're exactly where we need to be.

22:47.400 --> 22:49.500
我觉得太热了 斯科菲尔德
Heat's getting to me, Scofield.

22:49.600 --> 22:51.000
该休息了
It's quitting time.

22:58.900 --> 23:01.590
你介意告诉我 他怎么会在这里吗
You mind telling me why he's even out here with us?

23:01.600 --> 23:03.500
他猜到点什么
He knows something's up.

23:03.900 --> 23:05.190
该死的 他怎么会知道的
How the hell does he know that?

23:05.200 --> 23:07.000
只能说 我还是有点名气的
Let's just say I have a bit of a rep.

23:07.200 --> 23:08.800
因为福克斯河的事情?
From Fox River?

23:12.700 --> 23:14.300
我知道你是谁 伙计
I know who you are, mate.

23:14.400 --> 23:16.200
最近才知道的
Figured it out just lately.

23:16.600 --> 23:18.290
终于明白为什么他们会把你送进来
Finally made sense why they pick you

23:18.300 --> 23:19.800
而不是其他人
of all people to send here.

23:20.400 --> 23:21.800
别担心
No worries.

23:22.700 --> 23:25.100
保管你的小秘密 对我有好处
It's in my interest to keep your little secret.

23:25.100 --> 23:26.190
但是贝利克?
But Bellick?

23:26.200 --> 23:27.900
不能相信他
Can't be trusted.

23:29.000 --> 23:30.790
我可以搞定贝利克
I can handle Bellick.

23:30.800 --> 23:32.500
他不在计划内
He's not in on this.

23:32.500 --> 23:34.690
好 好吧
Okay, good.

23:34.700 --> 23:36.100
但是马宏在
But Mahone is.

23:36.700 --> 23:37.900
马宏?
Mahone?

23:38.400 --> 23:40.090
他像个病猫似的
He's looking abouts stable as a three-legged chair,

23:40.100 --> 23:41.290
他要跟我们一起越狱?
and he's escaping with us?

23:41.300 --> 23:43.300
不 只是他自己那么以为
No, he just thinks he is.

23:43.600 --> 23:44.990
他需要镇静剂
He needs his meds.

23:45.000 --> 23:47.690
否则他会疯掉
Without them, he'll self destruct.

23:47.700 --> 23:49.500
只是时间问题
It's just a matter of time.

23:51.300 --> 23:52.700
要是他没疯呢
And if he doesn't?

23:52.800 --> 23:55.500
我会骗他 告诉他他想知道的
I'll string him along, tell him what he wants to hear,

23:56.000 --> 23:57.700
然后摆脱他
and then I'll cut him loose.

23:59.200 --> 24:01.800
我怎么知道你不会对我做同样的事?
How do I know you're not going to do the same thing to me?

24:02.100 --> 24:03.500
你不用知道
You don't.

24:18.600 --> 24:20.500
需要帮助吗 我的朋友
You need a hook-up, my friend?

24:24.200 --> 24:24.590
不用了
No.

24:24.600 --> 24:26.090
别着急
Take your time.

24:26.100 --> 24:27.600
我可不强买强卖
I don't hard sell.

24:27.900 --> 24:29.890
我的货品不会让你后悔的
My pduct speaks for itself.

24:29.900 --> 24:33.490
在外面 我使用一些药品
Outside, I took something.

24:33.500 --> 24:38.290
一些需要医师处方才可买到的药 叫Varatril
It's a prescription drug called Varatril,

24:38.300 --> 24:40.700
我在想 你是不是可以
and I was wondering if you

24:41.300 --> 24:42.890
这里可没药房
This ain't no farmacia.

24:42.900 --> 24:45.500
但是我这有
But what I got right here

24:45.700 --> 24:47.090
比所有美国医生给你的东西
it's bter than anything your doctor

24:47.100 --> 24:48.800
还要好
gave you back in the States.

24:49.400 --> 24:50.190
那是焦油
That's tar.

24:50.200 --> 24:53.090
来尝尝 就一点
Just take a taste, algo pequenito.

24:53.100 --> 24:55.300
你知道的 要有约束
You know, keep it in check.

24:55.400 --> 24:57.300
我现在没钱
I don't have any money right now.

24:58.500 --> 24:59.990
那我也没药
Then I don't have any drugs.

25:00.000 --> 25:02.690
但是对个男人来说 在索纳
But there are a few ways for a man

25:02.700 --> 25:04.090
还是有些办法可以赚点小钱的
to make a few dollars in Sona

25:04.100 --> 25:05.690
满足其他人的需要
servicing the needs of others

25:05.700 --> 25:06.690
我个人是不感兴趣
not something I'm into

25:06.700 --> 25:08.300
你觉得我是个废物?
You think I'm a punk?

25:12.100 --> 25:12.890
我只是在帮你
I'm just helping you

25:12.900 --> 25:15.800
好起来 朋友 只是帮你好起来
get well, friend, just helping you get well.

25:24.000 --> 25:25.500
勒齐先生
Ser Lechero?

25:27.000 --> 25:28.500
勒齐先生
Ser Lechero.

25:29.400 --> 25:30.390
你想要什么
What do you want?

25:30.400 --> 25:32.290
我知道你是大忙人 但我想告诉你
Look, I know you're a busy man, but I wanted to tell ya,

25:32.300 --> 25:33.390
我不知道迈克·斯科菲尔德到底在干什么
I don't know exactly what he's doing,

25:33.400 --> 25:36.600
-但他只是拿你做垫脚石 -不是的 猪
but Michael Scofield's taking you for a ride. No, cerdo,

25:36.600 --> 25:37.590
我不那么认为
I don't think so.

25:37.600 --> 25:40.190
听着 昨天我听他说关于越狱的事
Listen, I heard him talking about escape yesterday

25:40.200 --> 25:42.490
-关于逃离这里 -他说要越狱
about breaking outta here. It's he's talking about escape,

25:42.500 --> 25:45.000
为什么你跑来告诉我 而不是跟他一起
why are you here telling me and you're not going with him, eh?

25:47.300 --> 25:49.490
如果他肯我当然愿意 但是他已拒绝我了
I would if he'd let me, but he's already cut me out.

25:49.500 --> 25:50.490
他说他没事 但是我知道
